---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Jobs">
  <Hero 
    title="Join The Rebellion" 
    subtitle="We're looking for marketing rebels who want to change the game"
  />
  
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="jobs-intro">
        <h2 class="section-title">Work With Us</h2>
        <p class="intro-text">True Brew Birdie isn't for everyone. We're looking for rebels, rule-breakers, and visionaries who are tired of marketing-as-usual and want to build something that actually matters.</p>
        
        <div class="culture-statement">
          <h3>Our Culture</h3>
          <p>We don't do corporate hierarchies. We don't do micromanagement. We don't do busywork.</p>
          <p>We do freedom. We do impact. We do work that matters.</p>
          <p>If you're looking for a 9-to-5 where you can hide in meetings and coast by on mediocrity, we're not for you.</p>
          <p>But if you want to build marketing systems that change industries and give entrepreneurs true freedom, keep reading.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="benefits-section">
        <h3 class="benefits-title">Why Join Our Rebellion?</h3>
        
        <div class="benefits-grid">
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">üåç</div>
            <h4 class="benefit-title">Work From Anywhere</h4>
            <p>We're a fully remote team spread across the globe. Work from home, a caf√©, or a beach in Bali‚Äîwe don't care as long as you deliver results.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">üí∞</div>
            <h4 class="benefit-title">Competitive Compensation</h4>
            <p>We pay above market rates because we expect above market results. Plus profit sharing for team members who drive exceptional growth.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">‚è∞</div>
            <h4 class="benefit-title">Flexible Hours</h4>
            <p>We care about results, not when you clock in. Set your own schedule and work when you're most productive.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">üìà</div>
            <h4 class="benefit-title">Growth Opportunities</h4>
            <p>Learn from industry disruptors, get mentored by our leadership team, and develop skills that put you years ahead of your peers.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">üß†</div>
            <h4 class="benefit-title">Continuous Learning</h4>
            <p>$2,500 annual learning budget for courses, books, conferences, and tools that help you level up your skills.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">üîã</div>
            <h4 class="benefit-title">Recharge Time</h4>
            <p>Unlimited PTO (that we actually encourage you to use) plus company-wide shutdown weeks to ensure everyone gets proper rest.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="openings-section">
        <h3 class="openings-title">Current Openings</h3>
        
        <div class="job-listings">
          <div class="job-card">
            <h4 class="job-title">AI Marketing Strategist</h4>
            <p class="job-location">Remote (Global)</p>
            <div class="job-description">
              <p>We're looking for someone who understands both the technical capabilities of AI and the creative aspects of marketing to help build our next generation of marketing systems.</p>
              <h5>What You'll Do:</h5>
              <ul>
                <li>Develop AI-powered marketing strategies for our clients</li>
                <li>Create frameworks that blend human creativity with machine efficiency</li>
                <li>Work with our tech team to build proprietary AI marketing tools</li>
                <li>Stay on the cutting edge of AI developments in marketing</li>
              </ul>
              <h5>What You Need:</h5>
              <ul>
                <li>3+ years experience in marketing strategy</li>
                <li>Deep understanding of AI tools and capabilities</li>
                <li>Ability to think both creatively and analytically</li>
                <li>Passion for pushing boundaries and breaking rules</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn">Apply Now</a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="job-card">
            <h4 class="job-title">Disruptive Copywriter</h4>
            <p class="job-location">Remote (Europe/US Timezones)</p>
            <div class="job-description">
              <p>We need a copywriter who doesn't just write words‚Äîthey craft narratives that shake industries and build movements.</p>
              <h5>What You'll Do:</h5>
              <ul>
                <li>Create compelling brand stories and marketing copy</li>
                <li>Develop voice and messaging frameworks for rebellious brands</li>
                <li>Write high-converting sales copy that doesn't feel like marketing</li>
                <li>Collaborate with our strategy team to ensure messaging aligns with growth goals</li>
              </ul>
              <h5>What You Need:</h5>
              <ul>
                <li>Portfolio of work that demonstrates your unique voice</li>
                <li>Understanding of direct response principles</li>
                <li>Ability to adapt your writing to different brand voices</li>
                <li>Hatred for generic, template-based marketing copy</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn">Apply Now</a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="job-card">
            <h4 class="job-title">Growth Systems Architect</h4>
            <p class="job-location">Remote (Global)</p>
            <div class="job-description">
              <p>We're looking for someone who can design and implement scalable marketing systems that generate predictable, consistent growth.</p>
              <h5>What You'll Do:</h5>
              <ul>
                <li>Build end-to-end marketing systems for our clients</li>
                <li>Implement automation workflows that scale with business growth</li>
                <li>Develop frameworks for lead generation, nurturing, and conversion</li>
                <li>Continuously optimize systems based on performance data</li>
              </ul>
              <h5>What You Need:</h5>
              <ul>
                <li>Experience building marketing systems that scale</li>
                <li>Deep understanding of marketing automation tools</li>
                <li>Data-driven approach to optimization</li>
                <li>Ability to see both the big picture and the technical details</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn">Apply Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="application-section">
        <h3 class="application-title">Don't See Your Role?</h3>
        <p>If you're a marketing rebel who wants to join our mission but don't see a role that fits, we still want to hear from you. Tell us how you can help us build the future of marketing.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-large">Create Your Own Role</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 900;
  }
  
  .jobs-intro {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
  }
  
  .intro-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .culture-statement {
    background-color: var(--color-dark-gray);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 5px;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    text-align: left;
  }
  
  .culture-statement h3 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-yellow);
  }
  
  .culture-statement p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .benefits-section {
    margin: 5rem 0;
  }
  
  .benefits-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-yellow);
  }
  
  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .benefit-card {
    background-color: var(--color-dark-gray);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 5px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .benefit-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }
  
  .benefit-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .benefit-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }
  
  .openings-section {
    margin: 5rem 0;
  }
  
  .openings-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-yellow);
  }
  
  .job-listings {
    display: grid;
    gap: 3rem;
  }
  
  .job-card {
    background-color: var(--color-dark-gray);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 5px;
  }
  
  .job-title {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-red);
  }
  
  .job-location {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-white);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  
  .job-description {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .job-description p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .job-description h5 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem;
    color: var(--color-yellow);
  }
  
  .job-description ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .job-description li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .application-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 5rem 0;
    padding: 3rem;
    background-color: var(--color-dark-gray);
    border-radius: 5px;
  }
  
  .application-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-yellow);
  }
  
  .application-section p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }
  
  .btn-large {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>
